         <abstract id="aspace_77a4743e5cea4c63d6ec588beadde45a">An artificial collection of leaflets, radio scripts, newspapers, and posters produced by American, Chinese, and Korean governments for use during the Korean War as propaganda devices.</abstract>
    
      </did>
